{"type":"article","id":2375,"title":"【美食】粉紅應該怎麼吃？","uid":4630,"topics":[2473,2474,1806,2475,2396,959],"contents":"劉仲敬《<a href=\"https://medium.com/@LiuZhongjing/%E6%9F%A5%E7%89%B9%E8%90%8A%E5%A4%AB%E4%BA%BA%E5%81%87%E8%A8%AD%E5%92%8C%E5%BC%B5%E7%8D%BB%E5%BF%A0%E5%81%87%E8%A8%AD-4007e277ef5c\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">查特萊夫人假設和張獻忠假設</a>》：<br>\n<blockquote>現代東亞核心區居民當中，有許多潛在而不自知的張獻忠。他們像年輕時期的查特萊夫人自以為厭惡性慾一樣，自以為厭惡人肉，然而一旦身體直接接觸人肉的刺激，就會發現自己的身體離不開人肉，像歷史人物朱桀和張獻忠一樣，即使在沒有饑餓威脅的情況下，都捨不得放棄人肉的美味，而且用各種美食家才了解細節的烹調技術，製作和保存了大量人肉食品，直到自己去世都沒有吃完。</blockquote><br>\n我也有<mark>支</mark>那血統，我也想吃小粉紅！習主席您快加速啊，趕快將中國推向新時代，我就可以帶著小伙伴們遊歷長江南北、獵殺小粉紅臘！！！<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/I73ZLvh.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/I73ZLvh.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/I73ZLvh.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n我想嘗試的幾種食法：<br>\n<br>\n北姑蒸香滑小粉紅（配飯）：<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/ALychRm.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ALychRm.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/ALychRm.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n（來源：<a href=\"https://www.pinterest.com/pin/507499451749904663/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Jac Pang</a>）<br>\n<br>\n港式咖哩小粉紅：<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/qqrGLm8.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qqrGLm8.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/qqrGLm8.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n（來源：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/torontofoolsblog/posts/429014987903184/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">香港人開飯同盟</a>）<br>\n<br>\n小粉紅蜜汁叉燒：<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Tkz7B3h.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Tkz7B3h.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Tkz7B3h.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n（來源：<a href=\"http://m.tesegu.com/techan/25858.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">特色谷</a>）<br>\n<br>\n玫瑰豉油小粉紅：<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/lKYpadL.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lKYpadL.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/lKYpadL.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n（來源：<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%B1%89%E6%B2%B9%E9%9B%9E\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">餵雞百科</a>）<br>\n<br>\n鐵板小粉紅鋸扒：<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/A2atkM0.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/A2atkM0.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/A2atkM0.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n（來源：<a href=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/759353/dining/%E9%8B%B8%E6%89%92-%E9%90%B5%E6%9D%BF%E9%A4%90-%E7%89%9B%E6%89%92-%E9%87%91%E9%B3%B3/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">新假期</a>）<br>\n<br>\n各位膜乎的食人族<b><u>同胞</u></b>心動不心動哇！快在問題下面寫回答，一起分享粉紅美食！政治規矩是寫回答必須貼圖！<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/gVIV5LP.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gVIV5LP.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/gVIV5LP.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-06-19","agreeCount":6,"discussionCount":0}